<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Optimiste Group — Platfòm Pwodwi Teknoloji</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0A1F44;
    --blue: #1565C0;
    --sky: #42A5F5;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --light: #E8F4FD;
    --gray: #8BA3C7;
  }
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; background: var(--navy); color: var(--white); overflow-x: hidden; }
  nav { position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 100; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 20px 40px; background: rgba(10,31,68,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(66,165,245,0.15); }
  .nav-logo { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--white); letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .nav-logo span { color: var(--sky); }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a { color: var(--gray); text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; transition: color 0.3s; }
  .nav-btn { background: var(--sky); color: var(--navy); border: none; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer; }
  .hero { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 120px 40px 80px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -200px; right: -200px; width: 700px; height: 700px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(21,101,192,0.3) 0%, transparent 70%); border-radius: 50%; animation: pulse 6s ease-in-out infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { transform: scale(1.1); } }
  .hero-content { max-width: 700px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .hero-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: rgba(66,165,245,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(66,165,245,0.3); padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--sky); letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  h1 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 80px); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.05; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  h1 .accent { color: var(--sky); }
  .hero-desc { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--gray); max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--sky); color: var(--navy); padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; text-decoration: none; }
  .btn-outline { border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); color: var(--white); padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 15px; text-decoration: none; }
  .stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
  .stat { padding: 40px; text-align: center; background: var(--navy); }
  .stat-num { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 42px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--sky); display: block; }
  .stat-label { color: var(--gray); font-size: 13px; }
  section { padding: 100px 40px; }
  .section-tag { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--sky); margin-bottom: 16px; display: block; }
  h2 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 52px); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .services { background: rgba(21,101,192,0.05); }
  .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; margin-top: 60px; }
  .service-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 20px; padding: 36px; transition: all 0.3s; }
  .service-icon { width: 56px; height: 56px; background: rgba(66,165,245,0.15); border-radius: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .service-card h3 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .service-card p { color: var(--gray); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; margin-top: 60px; }
  .step { display: flex; gap: 32px; padding: 40px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
  .step-num { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 64px; font-weight: 800; color: rgba(66,165,245,0.15); min-width: 80px; }
  .step h3 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .step p { color: var(--gray); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .contact { background: rgba(21,101,192,0.08); text-align: center; }
  .contact-card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(21,101,192,0.3), rgba(66,165,245,0.1)); border: 1px solid rgba(66,165,245,0.2); border-radius: 28px; padding: 80px 40px; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .contact-email { display: inline-block; color: var(--sky); font-size: 18px; margin: 32px 0; text-decoration: none; }
  footer { padding: 40px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .footer-logo { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 18px; }
  .footer-logo span { color: var(--sky); }
  footer p { color: var(--gray); font-size: 13px; }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { nav { padding: 16px 20px; } .nav-links { display: none; } .hero { padding: 100px 20px 60px; } section { padding: 70px 20px; } .stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .step { flex-direction: column; } footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; text-align: center; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">Optimiste<span>.</span></div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#services">Sèvis</a></li>
    <li><a href="#comment">Kijan</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Kontakt</a></li>
  </ul>
  <button class="nav-btn">Kòmanse →</button>
</nav>
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge">Platfòm Teknoloji Ayiti</div>
    <h1>Konekte Biznis<br>ak <span class="accent">Opòtinite</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">Optimiste Group devlope solisyon dijital entèlijan pou fasilite kominikasyon, vant, ak kwasans biznis nan mache lokal ak entènasyonal.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Kontakte Nou</a>
      <a href="#services" class="btn-outline">Dekouvri Sèvis yo →</a>
