  <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">2</span><span class="stat-label">Mache — Lokal & Entènasyonal</span></div>
  <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">24/7</span><span class="stat-label">Sipò Disponib</span></div>
</div>
<section class="services" id="services">
  <span class="section-tag">Sa Nou Ofri</span>
  <h2>Sèvis Nou yo</h2>
  <div class="services-grid">
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon">🌐</div><h3>Platfòm Dijital</h3><p>Kreye vizibilite pou pwodwi inovatè ou yo sou yon platfòm pwofesyonèl ki rive toupatou.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon">🤝</div><h3>Koneksyon Kliyan</h3><p>Nou sèvi kòm pon ant kliyan ak propriétaire pou fasilite transaksyon ak kominikasyon.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon">📈</div><h3>Kwasans Biznis</h3><p>Estrateji ak zouti pou ede biznis ou grandi nan mache lokal ak entènasyonal.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon">💬</div><h3>Kominikasyon Entèlijan</h3><p>Solisyon dijital pou amelyore kominikasyon ant ekip ou ak kliyan ou yo.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon">🛒</div><h3>Fasilitasyon Vant</h3><p>Platfòm vant entèlijan ki fè li fasil pou ou vann pwodwi ou yo nenpòt kote.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon">🔒</div><h3>Sekirite & Konfyans</h3><p>Teknoloji modèn ki pwoteje done ou ak asire tranzaksyon ou yo san risk.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="comment">
  <span class="section-tag">Pwosesis Nou</span>
  <h2>Kijan Sa Travay?</h2>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">01</div><div><h3>Enskri Biznis ou</h3><p>Kreye yon pwofil pou biznis ou sou platfòm nan.</p></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">02</div><div><h3>Prezante Pwodwi ou</h3><p>Platfòm nan montre pwodwi ou yo bay milye de kliyan potansyèl.</p></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">03</div><div><h3>Resevwa Kliyan</h3><p>Kliyan kontakte ou dirèkteman nan sèkirite.</p></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">04</div><div><h3>Grandi ak Nou</h3><p>Itilize done ak estrateji nou ba ou pou devlope biznis ou.</p></div></div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="contact" id="contact">
  <div class="contact-card">
    <span class="section-tag">Kontakte Nou</span>
    <h2>Prè pou Kòmanse?</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-top:16px;">Ekip nou an la pou ede ou. Voye nou yon imel epi nou ap reponn ou rapidman.</p>
    <a href="mailto:isteah.ptoussaint14@gmail.com" class="contact-email">isteah.ptoussaint14@gmail.com</a><br>
    <a href="mailto:isteah.ptoussaint14@gmail.com" class="btn-primary" style="display:inline-block; margin-top:16px;">Voye Imel Kounye a →</a>
  </div>
</section>
<footer>
  <div class="footer-logo">Optimiste<span> Group</span></div>
  <p>© 2026 Optimiste Group. Tout dwa rezève.</p>
  <p style="color:var(--sky);">Ayiti 🇭🇹</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
